The Gaderffii, or Gaffi Stick, is a short, staff-like weapon traditional to the native Sand People of Tatooine. Featuring a heavy, blunt-spiked club head at one end and a set of metal blades with another spike at the other, they are brutally effective multi-purpose tools.
